data.description: Welcome to the lowest price per square foot in a beautiful subdivision!  This Home has 4 bedrooms plus an office!  Did you see the amazing pool?  The lot is also oversized due to being on a cul-de-sac and boasts no back neighbors!!  You get access to all community amenities, which include a dock overlooking the pond stocked with fish for fishing.  Multiple playgrounds, walking grounds, and private community pool.  Reach out today for your private tour!
